articles.title: 20-year-old amateur Nick Dunlap withdraws from Farmers Insurance Open after historic win - Yahoo Sports
articles.description: Nick Dunlap became the first amateur to win on the PGA Tour since 1991 on Sunday when he won the American Express.
articles.content:
Nick Dunlap wont be headed to San Diego this week after all.
